{"tid":1218792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【職業軍人見解】港警心理分析","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T18:19:41.000Z","uid":258326,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6f1175b6f990c27ac126a4486e3d5fc1f4617b","tid":1218792,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"下面嘅討論係喺某個我成日睇嘅台藉美軍FB度見到，本來個post係講佢對「港警應該將槍口提高一公分」嘅睇法。如果大家有關注開台灣軍事，應該知呢位係邊個，但我費時公開人私隱了。Anyway，講呢啲不過係想話佢的確係軍人，而且曾喺2003年去過伊拉克打過仗，所以我認為係有參考價值。<br />\n<br />\n如果嫌長，總括而言就係一句：<strong>佢認同港警開槍，而且呢個係台灣甚至外國軍警界嘅普遍態度。</strong> 佢認為人性本來脆弱，一旦去到開槍嘅地步，射手通常已經處於無法理智思考嘅狀況，因此會反射性地作出由日常訓練灌注入腦嘅動作（瞄準致命部位 &gt; 開火）。外國軍人亦誤以為香港的示威者同外國示威者/ 武裝分子用嘅武力一樣。<br />\n<br />\n台藉美軍 = A生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EH8udWx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEH8udWx.png&h=266ddb47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人唔同意佢講法，引起一長串討論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZ5sK7m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZ5sK7m.png&h=62646d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8NdxWdd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8NdxWdd.png&h=96947c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsRvHTi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsRvHTi.png&h=777e204f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/behCnTn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbehCnTn.png&h=12496d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一位回覆者係台藉法國外藉兵團成員（夏生），前身為海龍蛙兵。同樣，關注開台灣軍事嘅人應該知呢位係邊個。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0UxbOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0UxbOw.png&h=83680bd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0f31d405931e65e2458afc234997f8351a5d2a3","tid":1218792,"uid":2507,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"拎打仗同前日嚟比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家陣班示威人士威脅到警察生命？ 有冇學工聯會整🍍呀？"},{"pid":"4ae081fa521a70358e8f3b17099aaad9893353bb","tid":1218792,"uid":258326,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e0f31d405931e65e2458afc234997f8351a5d2a3","tid":1218792,"uid":2507,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"拎打仗同前日嚟比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家陣班示威人士威脅到警察生命？ 有冇學工聯會整🍍呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"呢個就係重點<br />\n外國人唔知，以為同佢哋嗰種一樣。"},{"pid":"402dfa59bd354da4aedef578e90d324fd4e231a6","tid":1218792,"uid":85659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"呢d咪叫正撚宗 鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n台仔玩軍武10個11個都係大中華膠黎"},{"pid":"e12e1bc391b55edacb7592027992e8a07863bb09","tid":1218792,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"402dfa59bd354da4aedef578e90d324fd4e231a6","tid":1218792,"uid":85659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"呢d咪叫正撚宗 鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n台仔玩軍武10個11個都係大中華膠黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"佢係退伍美軍，講佢大美國可能仲啱啲，但一定唔係大中華。"},{"pid":"1da7def3c4072f3708de50d818a848ec2f99acdf","tid":1218792,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"402dfa59bd354da4aedef578e90d324fd4e231a6","tid":1218792,"uid":85659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"呢d咪叫正撚宗 鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n台仔玩軍武10個11個都係大中華膠黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"更正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩就台仔一定玩過<br />\n宅先岩<br />\n屌你 宅呢飯既真係忽忽地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舉個例<br />\n美國軍售<br />\n佢地係見到坦克車會扯旗<br />\n但係飛彈就嫌多個類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09990e5ce990c49500ac83927e784e1490ff3f05","tid":1218792,"uid":189,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:03:47.000Z","msg":"咩軍人面對敵人嘅武器係膠樽，遮，磚頭？<br />\n我諗應該得支那同印度"},{"pid":"3b85912e8df6dc045